title: Wonderburg [FINAL] [www.hellenic-world.net]
description:
Wonderburg Ghost pirates, curses, and spells abound in the fantastic 
world of Wonderburg!

But never fear, you have the aid of a trusty witch and a stalwart 
dwarf as you restore order to a city fallen into chaos.

Snarling dragons, nefarious wizards, and civil unrest are only a 
few issues plaguing these citizens and only you can save the day!

* Charming visuals
* Beautiful hand drawn story sequences
* Colorful, fantasy-themed environments
